org.apache.flink.util

接口 IterableIterator<E>

  • 类型参数:
    E - The iterated elements' type.
    所有超级接口:
    Iterable<E>, Iterator<E>

    @Internal
public interface IterableIterator<E>
extends Iterator<E>, Iterable<E>
    An Iterator that is also Iterable (often by returning itself).

    • 方法概要

      • 从接口继承的方法 java.util.Iterator

        forEachRemaining, hasNext, next, remove

      • 从接口继承的方法 java.lang.Iterable

        forEach, iterator, spliterator
